Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:22.00,Default,1,0,0,0,A,The old Lion and the Fox
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:31.50,Default,2,0,0,0,S,Once upon a time in the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:31.50,Default,2,0,0,0,E,there lived a lion who had grown very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:36.00,Default,3,0,0,0,S,The lion's teeth and claws were worn with old age
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:39.50,Default,3,0,0,0,E,and he couldn't hunt for food anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:44.50,Default,4,0,0,0,S,One day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.50,Default,4,0,0,0,M,he got an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:49.44,Default,4,0,0,0,E,and sent a message to everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:00.28,Default,5,0,0,0,A,He pretended to be sick and summoned everyone to come and visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:09.50,Default,6,0,0,0,S,The next day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:09.52,Default,6,0,0,0,E,the goat came to the lion's cave to offer its sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.38,Default,7,0,0,0,S,But as soon as the goat walked in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.60,Default,7,0,0,0,E,the lion caught and ate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.02,Default,8,0,0,0,A,A deer came to the cave the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:24.12,Default,9,0,0,0,S,But as he walked in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:24.12,Default,9,0,0,0,E,the lion got him and ate him as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:33.62,Default,10,0,0,0,S,One by one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:33.62,Default,10,0,0,0,E,the lion ate the animals who came to visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:40.16,Default,11,0,0,0,S,One day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:40.16,Default,11,0,0,0,E,the clever fox came outside the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.86,Default,12,0,0,0,S,The fox was very cautious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:46.66,Default,12,0,0,0,E,and stood at a safe distance from the cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:52.38,Default,13,0,0,0,A,Then he enquired politely about the lion's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.38,Default,14,0,0,0,S,The lion replied that he was very well indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:58.04,Default,14,0,0,0,E,and asked the fox to step in for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:01.26,Default,15,0,0,0,S,The fox wisely stayed outside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:05.16,Default,15,0,0,0,E,thanking the lion very kindly for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.78,Default,16,0,0,0,A,"I should be glad to do as you ask."he added.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:14.70,Default,17,0,0,0,S,"But I have noticed that there are too many footprints leading to your cave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.84,Default,17,0,0,0,E,but there are no marks of anyone coming out."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:22.72,Default,18,0,0,0,S,"Please tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:22.72,Default,18,0,0,0,E,how do your visitors find their way out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:27.94,Default,19,0,0,0,S,The lion realized that he couldn't fool the fox
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:27.94,Default,19,0,0,0,E,who was very wise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:37.50,Default,20,0,0,0,S,The fox then went back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.92,Default,20,0,0,0,E,and told everyone what the lion was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.14,Default,21,0,0,0,S,He was saved
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.68,Default,21,0,0,0,E,only because he learned from the mistakes of others.
